snippet.title: When to Let Go Full Version | Amber Marshall and Shaun Johnston | Heartland 1004 | CBC
snippet.description:
Listen to the full version of "When to Let Go", as featured on Episode 1004 of Heartland.

Watch the full episode on CBC Gem: http://bit.ly/3bdzk9M

About Heartland: Heartland is a family drama on CBC TV about a family dealing with the highs and lows of life on a horse ranch in the stunning the foothills of Alberta.
